    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Gryllotalpa hirsuta Burmeister, 1838 (A, B) and Gryllotalpa siamensis Giebel, 1870 (C) male habitus in dorsal view with the specimen labels: labelled AGryhirS 01 (A, B) and BG 00071 S 01 (C, D) and AGrysiaS 01 (E, F). Images from DORSA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220555/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220556>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Gryllotalpa hirsuta Burmeister, 1838 (A, B) and Gryllotalpa siamensis Giebel, 1870 (C) male tegmina: labelled AGryhirS 01 (A) and labelled BG 00071 S 01 (B) and AGrysiaS 01 (C) in dorsal view. Images from DORSA." ;
